{"tid":231382,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]懷疑同事暗戀我...又或者其實係我暗戀緊佢?","createTime":"2017-05-06T04:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T04:08:37.000Z","uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1c5540d993208b3fda481b8d382ae1be245101","tid":231382,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"人工低工時長包食宿<br />\n咩工就唔好問啦<br />\n學到好多野但就要同另一個同事成日一齊瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁叫佢Y啦<br />\n一開始同Y唔係好熟 佢望落去蠢蠢地,又冇咩共通話題<br />\n做野者,又唔係做人世,是但啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一晚一齊瞓簡直地獄,我feel到我同Y都全身僵硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大家都好難瞓著,<br />\n點解會得一張床架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿頭叫我lead Y做野,因為佢0經驗    <span style=\"font-size: small;\">0經驗都請</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左幾日開始熟,傾開運動原來Y有玩開BJJ,難怪個BODY操得咁勁 <span style=\"color: blue;\">不過我都唔輸蝕</span><br />\n我唔知佢係特登定點,成日都有意無意有身體接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 埋到頭撞頭咁,瞓覺果時伸晒手手腳腳過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我緊係推開佢啦&quot;屌你咩<br />\n 彈撚開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot; 推推下慣左就冇再推...<br />\n<br />\n其實呢度都只係一兩個星期的事, <br />\n呢排Y要遠征打比賽請左一星期假<br />\n期間係音訊全無<br />\n恐怖嘅係...我發現...............走左兩日我已經開始掛住Y <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca3ca3a1a8cd1527dcbf8febf8c4f54852d031c","tid":231382,"uid":47184,"like":0,"disl